import sys
import threading

def solve():
    import sys
    data = sys.stdin.read().split()
    it = iter(data)
    n = int(next(it)); k = int(next(it))
    adj = [[] for _ in range(n+1)]
    for _ in range(n-1):
        a = int(next(it)); b = int(next(it))
        adj[a].append(b)
        adj[b].append(a)
    parent = [0]*(n+1)
    order = []
    stack = [1]
    parent[1]= -1
    while stack:
        v = stack.pop()
        order.append(v)
        for u in adj[v]:
            if parent[u]==0:
                parent[u]=v
                stack.append(u)
    size = [1]*(n+1)
    for v in reversed(order):
        p = parent[v]
        if p>0:
            size[p]+=size[v]
    score = [0]*(n+1)
    for i in range(1,n+1):
        score[i] = i - (size[i]-1)
    nodes = list(range(1,n+1))
    nodes.sort(key=lambda x: score[x], reverse=True)
    removed = set(nodes[:k])
    res = sorted(removed)
    print(" ".join(map(str,res)))
